 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">为了给您提供更好的游戏体验并活跃游戏气氛，让您结识更多的游戏伙伴、体验更多的挑战，37《大天使之剑》顺应广大玩家的需求将进行合服维护，合服完成后玩家可以通过原有账号登陆数据互通后的服务器。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">【合服规则】</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">一、堆积账号清理规则</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">1.为了优化服务器环境，给各位玩家营造更好的游戏环境，我们决定在进行数据互通的同时，对长时间没有登陆的游戏角色进行清理，满足以下全部条件的角色将被作为堆积账号，具体的判断规则如下：</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">a)等级小于等于大师200级</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">b)没有进行过充值</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">c)最近7天没有登录记录</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">例：玩家等级9级且未充值且7天内没有进行过登陆则会在数据互通中被删除。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">注意：被清理的角色资料将全部删除，且官方不会对这些角色提供恢复服务，请各位玩家珍惜自己的游戏角色。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">二、基本规则</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">1.数据互通后玩家数据、物品、金币、任务、活跃度、钻石等信息完全保留。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">2.所有排行榜数据清空，开服后根据数据互通后的所有玩家数据重新进行排名（排行榜时效性称号被清空，到发称号时间根据角色排行情况重新发放）。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">3.所有战盟的状态（包括：成员、战盟等级、资金等）完全保留。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">4.合服后，等级奖励活动中可领取人数将以合服服务器中最早开服的服务器数据为准。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">三、特殊规则</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">1.数据互通后，如果在多个服务器同时拥有角色，玩家每次登陆账号的时候，选择登陆的区服，则会进入对应的角色(如在1、4区都有角色，1和4合并后，从4区进入的为4区角色)。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">2.数据互通后，充值的方式将按照原来的方式进行充值，如果1、2、3服互通在一起后，如果该账号三个服都创建了角色，充值时请自行选择需要充值的区服，即如果想要充值到1服的角色上，请在充值页面选择1服即可。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"conent-right\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: right;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">33娱乐运营团队</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 34px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\" data-v-0b53368b=\"\">2019年5月24日</p>\n</div>\n</div>', '2', '932', '', '1');
